sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant S as 👤 Student
    participant B as 🖥️ Browser
    participant F as ⚙️ Flask App
    participant TB as 🧠 TextBlob NLP
    participant AI as 💡 AI Suggestion Engine
    participant DB as 💾 SQLite Database
    participant SM as 📧 Gmail SMTP
    participant T as 👨‍🏫 Teacher

    S->>B: Fill feedback form (ratings + text)
    B->>F: POST /submit_feedback (AJAX)
    activate F
    F->>F: Validate input fields
    F->>TB: Analyze feedback text
    activate TB
    TB->>TB: Calculate polarity (-1.0 to +1.0)
    TB->>TB: Calculate subjectivity (0.0 to 1.0)
    TB-->>F: Return polarity, subjectivity
    deactivate TB
    F->>F: Classify sentiment (threshold check)
    F->>AI: Generate suggestions(text, sentiment)
    activate AI
    AI->>AI: Keyword matching analysis
    AI-->>F: Return suggestion list
    deactivate AI
    F->>DB: INSERT feedback record
    DB-->>F: Confirm stored (record ID)
    F->>SM: Send email notification
    SM-->>T: Email with feedback details
    SM-->>F: Delivery status (success)
    F-->>B: JSON response (sentiment, suggestions)
    deactivate F
    B-->>S: Display result with emoji indicator
